{"tid":49150,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[一人n個］分享玩命出事既經歷","createTime":"2016-12-21T13:26:48.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T18:06:36.000Z","uid":12696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"516e71cda10827489cdb2b8dcfe44933a64d6c2e","tid":49150,"uid":12696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T13:26:48.000Z","msg":"細個唔識死<br />\n中秋節同呀哥落街煲蠟<br />\n個陣唔知加左d咩愈煲愈勁<br />\n係個月餅罐入面d火高到半個人咁高<br />\n我地先開始識淆<br />\n諗住cum埋個蓋佢但唔成功<br />\n最後我呀哥一野踢我我個到<br />\n我左腳縮得切<br />\n右腳縮唔切跟住成隻腳燒撚著左<br />\n最後驚動d大人救番我<br />\n送左入醫院<br />\n事後洗左三個月腳<br />\n起哂膿<br />\nD同學仔成日抽水<br />\n話都話唔好煲蠟架啦,哥哥好痛呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea57ebfa9efdcfe78c1200805266257019b5ea1","tid":49150,"uid":53663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T13:28:18.000Z","msg":"19年前游水游太快"},{"pid":"688abb6d938807c11d2267a9a6ec5c4c613ddca6","tid":49150,"uid":18320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T13:29:55.000Z","msg":"屌你老母留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b38c96d99cffd816f269fc9737d9f738db5e8af","tid":49150,"uid":33640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T13:31:23.000Z","msg":"留名變鬼故post"},{"pid":"727f694fb14c2f831e3e04177b9cdb8686489f0d","tid":49150,"uid":59219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T13:54:29.000Z","msg":"細個唔知點解媽咪用熨斗可以熨得直啲衫<br />\n襯佢熨完行開咗 成隻手掌放落個熨斗到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲餘溫熱到我仆街 隻手起咗少少水泡<br />\n即刻嗌媽咪 好彩佢冇鬧我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f0ce3e380d53799c9d8dc08c1072875a6e47e11","tid":49150,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T13:55:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>19年前游水游太快</blockquote><br />\n起碼游贏其他果幾億條 證明你係優秀種"},{"pid":"b87da8943031e9220682a2e556f8ac16bb93176f","tid":49150,"uid":27309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T14:43:20.000Z","msg":"我係玩我細佬條命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽我媽咪講 我一歲幾 細佬仲係bb仔<br />\n媽咪比蘋果我食<br />\n我塞落細佬個口 差啲哽死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2153a6317c2a12122f92ec7ba005a7da93af435","tid":49150,"uid":54597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:10:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係玩我細佬條命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽我媽咪講 我一歲幾 細佬仲係bb仔<br />\n媽咪比蘋果我食<br />\n我塞落細佬個口 差啲哽死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a630c0bc617a042acca55f0c4db2f9ecbe1d0c8","tid":49150,"uid":31007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:38:52.000Z","msg":"小學嗰陣同同學去踩單車<br />\n喺個斜路度鬥快<br />\n點知個斜路盡頭係轉彎位<br />\n佢炒左車，一邊手流曬血<br />\n行近d,滿血嘅手肘位仲見到白色嘅野<br />\n嗰陣以為係骨嚟<br />\n之後佢入左院，話白色嗰d係肌肉嚟<br />\n令到我內疚左一排<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"760a14320906f353b8eb7045b9e6b5c190489289","tid":49150,"uid":17213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:50:03.000Z","msg":"細個唔識死，走去信教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://68.media.tumblr.com/548266014926e0933d88bb2bff5076eb/tumblr_oh28dekBR81s02vreo1_400.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F68.media.tumblr.com%2F548266014926e0933d88bb2bff5076eb%2Ftumblr_oh28dekBR81s02vreo1_400.gif&h=ecbcc7d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1e94d3ec91d13d9554fd20cbc26352ed654be07","tid":49150,"uid":55281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":